Name: The name of the class period (up to 50 char)
StartTime: The start time of the period (e.g. 8:00 or 11:35AM)
EndTime: The end time of the period (should be after the start time)
StartDate: The date of the first instance of this period (e.g. 9/1/2020, 09/03/20)
EndDate: The date until which this period repeats (e.g. 12/3/2020, 05/25/21)
ScheduleRuleType: Either ByDayOfWeek or ByDayOfWeekEveryOtherWeek - ByDayOfWeek uses the DaysOfWeek field for each week during the date range, ByDayOfWeekEveryOtherWeek will alternate weeks
DaysOfWeek: The list of days of the week which this period pertains (e.g. "Sunday,Wednesday,Saturday" or "Monday Tuesday Wednesday Thursday Friday")
Url: an optional URL to the virtual meeting location (up to 500 char)
